                                     height="400px"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     alt=""
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="about__col">
                            <ol class="about__list">
                                <li class="about__item">There were times when I rolled people underground, yes I was
                                    a subway driver))).
                                </li>
                                <li class="about__item">You won't believe it, I wrote the code in Russian, yes it
                                    was 1C, by the way, it's not so bad there, but it's boring.
                                </li>
                                <li class="about__item">There were other jobs, but somehow it all brought me here to
                                    the web.
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                            <a class="about__resume btn"
                               href="https://hh.ru/resume/e1aaa07eff016819120039ed1f74545a356245"
                               target="_blank">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
